HEADWORD: Inviting
<hw>In*vit"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Alluring; tempting;
<as>as, an <ex>inviting</ex> amusement or prospect</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Nothing is so easy and <qex>inviting</qex> as the retort of abuse
and sarcasm.</q> <rj><qau>W. Irving.</qau></rj></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>In*vit"ing*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>In*vit"ing*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms> <rj><au>Jer.
Taylor.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Invitrifiable</ent>⟦br⟧
